prompts.frontCover: Greeting card front cover, vibrant comic book art style. A dynamic and action-packed single panel scene titled "THE ADVENTURES OF SUPER JORDAN!" The cartoon illustrated man from the photo (Jordan) is depicted as a superhero, mid-air on a snowboard, grinning with confident excitement. He's wearing the dark t-shirt from the photo, but now with a flowing red superhero cape. The cartoon illustrated woman from the photo (Lao Lao) is riding on his back, laughing joyfully, wearing her white zip-up top. They are snowboarding down a snowy mountain slope made of cascading lines of binary code (0s and 1s). The background is a chaotic and humorous explosion of their favorite things: giant pieces of sushi, perfectly marbled wagyu steaks, and Chinese takeout boxes fly through the air amidst classic comic book action words like "KA-POW!" and "ZAP!". The scene is rendered with bold black outlines, halftone dot patterns for shading, and a vibrant, saturated color palette. Centered in the middle of the composition, a large, stylized speech bubble contains the text "Happy Birthday to my Favorite Superhero!" in a beautiful, readable, handwritten cursive script. 2D flat artwork, high detail.
